    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><small><strong><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/ai-for-nonprofits/\">AI Hub for Nonprofits</a> &gt; <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/ai-for-nonprofits/articles/\">Articles</a> &gt; Podcasts &gt; <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/ai-for-nonprofits/tools/\">Tools</a>\u00a0</strong></small></p>\n<hr />\n<h2>Episodes</h2>\n<p><span class=\"code char\"><span data-olk-copy-source=\"MessageBody\"><span dir=\"auto\">\u2022 <a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/the-ai-dilemma-with-tristan-harris-the-prof-g-pod/id1073226719?i=1000742450038\">The AI Dilemma</a> [Center for Humane Technology]</span><br />\n\u2022 </span></span><a href=\"https://bigduck.com/insights/how-can-you-put-ai-to-work-for-your-nonprofit\">How to Put AI to Work for Your Nonprofit</a> [Big Duck]<br />\n<span class=\"code char\"><span data-olk-copy-source=\"MessageBody\">\u2022</span></span> <a href=\"https://wholewhale.podbean.com/e/10-blue-links-era-is-over-create-ai-resistant-content-avinash-kaushik/\">The 10 Blue Links Era is Over</a> [Whole Whale]<br />\n\u2022 <a href=\"https://nonprofitnation.buzzsprout.com/1778536/episodes/18163549-how-ai-can-help-year-end-fundraising-overwhelm-with-tommy-vacek\">How AI Can Help Year-End Fundraising</a> \u00a0[Nonprofit Nation]<br />\n\u2022 <a href=\"https://joangarry.com/podcast/ai-for-nonprofit-success/\">The AI Field Guide: A Playbook for Nonprofit Success</a> [Nonprofits Are Messy]<br />\n\u2022 <a href=\"https://www.podbean.com/media/share/pb-nqrap-1868fa8?utm_campaign=w_share_ep&amp;utm_medium=dlink&amp;utm_source=w_share\">How Non-Profits are Using AI</a> \u00a0[Responsible Disruption]<br />\n\u2022\u00a0<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/episode/6ahG3s2bAImOCGYRfexwBj\">Predictive AI Unpacked</a> \u00a0[The AI Dude]<br />\n\u2022 <a href=\"https://the-ezra-klein-show.simplecast.com/episodes/nilay-patel\">Will AI Break the Internet? Or Save It?</a> [The Ezra Klein Show]<br />\n<span class=\"code char\">\u2022 </span><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2024/04/16/podcasts/the-daily/ai-data.html\">AI\u2019s Origi</a><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2024/04/16/podcasts/the-daily/ai-data.html\">nal Sin</a>\u00a0[The Daily]<br />\n<span class=\"code char\">\u2022 </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k6B1TTgxLw0\">AI For Good &#8211; But Is It?</a> [Turnkey for Good]</p>\n<h2>Series</h2>\n<p><span class=\"code char\">\u2022 <a href=\"https://fundraising.ai/all-podcast-episodes/\">FundraisingAI</a> with <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/nathanchappell/\">Nathan Chappell</a> and <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/scott-rosenkrans-916b9139/\">Scott Rosenkrans</a></span><br />\n<span class=\"code char\">\u2022 </span><a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/the-artificial-intelligence-show/id1548733275\">The Artificial Intelligence Show</a> with <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/paulroetzer/\">Paul Roetzer</a> and <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/mikekaput/\">Mike Kaput</a></p>\n<hr />\n<div style=\"background-color: #cdddf4; padding: 5px;\"><strong>To request a podcast be added to the list, please post it to our <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/groups/14431695/\">Artificial Intelligence (AI) for Nonprofit Organizations LinkedIn Group</a>.</strong></div>\n<hr />\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/certificate-programs/certificate-in-artificial-intelligence-ai-for-marketing-fundraising/\">2026 Certificate in Artificial Intelligence (AI) for Marketing &amp; Fundraising program</a> provides an honest, balanced approach to using AI for nonprofit marketing and fundraising\u2014and illuminates why AI literacy is a must-have skill for 2026 and onward. Customized for nonprofit professionals, this webinar series will expand your skill set, advance your career, and help transition your nonprofit into the age of AI.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/certificate-programs/certificate-in-artificial-intelligence-ai-for-marketing-fundraising/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-44090 size-full\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2026-Certificate-in-AI-for-Nonprofits-e1753375936499.png?resize=900%2C707&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"Certificate in AI for Marketing &amp; Fundraising awarded by Nonprofit Tech for Good, signed by CEO Heather Mansfield, with a blue award banner.\" width=\"900\" height=\"707\" /></a></p>\n",
